---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental JBR Dubai 2026 — From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals at JBR (Jumeirah Beach Residence). Beachside delivery. Economy from AED 35/day. High demand in April — book early."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 JBR — Jumeirah Beach Residence</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental JBR — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies at JBR and The Walk. Beachside pickup and delivery to your hotel or apartment.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=jbr" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get JBR Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=JBR+Dubai&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="JBR Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental at JBR</h2>
    <p>JBR (Jumeirah Beach Residence) is Dubai's most popular beachside district for tourists and short-stay visitors. Car rental demand at JBR peaks during events season — especially April with Art Dubai and the Boat Show driving visitor numbers up.</p>
    <p>Economy cars are available from AED 35/day with delivery to JBR tower lobbies. Most operators also cover The Walk, Bluewaters Island, and Ain Dubai area. Weekly rates work out cheaper at AED 200–350 for 7 days.</p>
    <p>JBR has good tram connectivity to Dubai Marina and Media City, but a car is essential for reaching attractions like Global Village, Desert Safari operators, and Abu Dhabi day trips.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
